<p class="ayah 5-15" id="15" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَـٰٓأَهْلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">O People</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْكِتَـٰبِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the Book!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَدْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Surely</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَآءَكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">has come to you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَسُولُنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Our Messenger</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُبَيِّنُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">making clear</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَثِيرًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">much</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّمَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُنتُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you used to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُخْفُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">conceal</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir