<p class="ayah 5-55" id="55" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Only</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلِيُّكُمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your ally</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَرَسُولُهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and His Messenger,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَامَنُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believe,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُقِيمُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">establish</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلصَّلَوٲةَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the prayer</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَيُؤْتُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and give</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلزَّكَوٲةَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">zakah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and they</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="