<p class="ayah 5-58" id="58" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَادَيْتُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you make a call</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلصَّلَوٲةِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the prayer,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱتَّخَذُوهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they take it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُزُوًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(in) ridicule</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَعِبًا‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and fun.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذَٲلِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">That</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِأَنَّهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) because they</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَوْمٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are) a people</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(who do) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَعْقِلُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">understand.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span cla