<p class="ayah 5-59" id="59" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَـٰٓأَهْلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`O People</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْكِتَـٰبِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the Book!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هَلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Do</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَنقِمُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you resent</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنَّآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[of] us</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">except</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَامَنَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">we believe</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُنزِلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">has been revealed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَيْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to us</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُنزِلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">was revealed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن قَبْلُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">before,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَكْثَرَكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">most of you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَـٰسِقُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are) defiantly disobedient.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>59<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 5-60" id="60" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هَلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Shall</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُنَبِّئُكُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">I inform you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِشَرٍّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) worse</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">than</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذَٲلِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَثُوبَةً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(as) recompense</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عِندَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah?</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Whom</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَّعَنَهُ ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah has cursed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَغَضِبَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and He became angry</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ع