<p class="ayah 5-61" id="61" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَآءُوكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they come to you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالُوٓاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَامَنَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`We believe.`</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَقَد</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">But certainly</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">دَّخَلُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they entered</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱلْكُفْرِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with disbelief</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and they</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَدْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">certainly</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَرَجُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">went out</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِهِۦ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with it.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quran