<p class="ayah 5-69" id="69" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَامَنُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هَادُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">became Jews</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلصَّـٰبِــُٔونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the Sabians</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلنَّصَـٰرَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the Christians,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">whoever</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَامَنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْيَوْمِ ٱلْأَخِرِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the Last Day</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَعَمِلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and did</span></span><span class="word stat