<p class="ayah 5-74" id="74" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَفَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So will not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَتُوبُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they repent</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَيَسْتَغْفِرُونَهُۥ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and seek His forgiveness?</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">غَفُورٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) Oft-Forgiving,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَّحِيمٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Most Merciful.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>74<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
