<p class="ayah 5-98" id="98" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱعْلَمُوٓاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Know</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَدِيدُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) severe</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْعِقَابِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(in) punishment</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">غَفُورٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) Oft-Forgiving,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَّحِيمٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Most Merciful.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>98<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 5-99" id="99" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">on</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلرَّسُولِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Messenger</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">except</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْبَلَـٰغُ‌ۗ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the conveyance.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَعْلَمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">knows</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُبْدُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you reveal</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَكْتُمُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you conceal.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>99<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 5-100" id="100" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُل</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَسْتَوِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are) equal</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْخَبِيثُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the evil</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلطَّيِّبُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the good</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَوْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">even if</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَعْجَبَكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">impresses you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَثْرَةُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">abundance</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْخَبِيثِ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the evil.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَٱتَّقُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So fear</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَـٰٓأُوْلِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">O men</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَلْبَـٰبِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) understanding,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَعَلَّكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">so that you may</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُفْلِحُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">be successful.`</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>100<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 5-101" id="101" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">O you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَامَنُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believe!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(Do) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَسْــَٔلُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">ask</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">about</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَشْيَآءَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">things</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">if</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُبْدَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">made clear</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to you,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَسُؤْكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">it may distress you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and if</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَسْــَٔلُواْ</spa