<p class="ayah 5-105" id="105" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">O you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَامَنُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believe!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Upon you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنفُسَكُمْ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is to guard) yourselves.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا يَضُرُّكُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Will not harm you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(those) who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ضَلَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(have gone) astray</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱهْتَدَيْتُمْ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you have been guided.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">To</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span 