<p class="ayah 5-107" id="107" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَإِنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then if</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عُثِرَ عَلَىٰٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">it is discovered</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنَّهُمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that the two</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱسْتَحَقَّآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(were) guilty</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِثْمًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) sin,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَـَٔـاخَرَانِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then (let) two others</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَقُومَانِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">stand</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَقَامَهُمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(in) their place</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱسْتَحَقَّ عَلَيْهِمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">have a lawful right over them -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَوْلَيَـٰنِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the former