<p class="ayah 5-108" id="108" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذَٲلِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">That</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَدْنَىٰٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) closer</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَأْتُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they will give</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱلشَّهَـٰدَةِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the testimony</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَىٰ وَجْهِهَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in its (true) form</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَوْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">or</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَخَافُوٓاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they would fear</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُرَدَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">will be refuted</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَيْمَـٰنُۢ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their oaths</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَعْدَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">after</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText