<p class="ayah 5-109" id="109" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">۞ يَوْمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(The) day</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَجْمَعُ ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah will gather</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلرُّسُلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Messengers</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَيَقُولُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and He will say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَاذَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`What</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُجِبْتُمْ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">was (the) response you received?`</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">They said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`(There is) no</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عِلْمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">knowledge</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَنَآ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for us.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed You,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنتَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">You</span></span><span class="word staticWor