<p class="ayah 5-110" id="110" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِذْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">When</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالَ ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَـٰعِيسَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`O Isa,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱبْنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">son</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَرْيَمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) Maryam!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱذْكُرْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Remember</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نِعْمَتِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">My Favor</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">upon you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَعَلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and upon</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٲلِدَتِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your mother</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِذْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَيَّدتُّكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">I strengthened you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" di