<p class="ayah 5-114" id="114" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Said</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عِيسَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Isa,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱبْنُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">son</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَرْيَمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) Maryam,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهُمَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`O Allah,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبَّنَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">our Lord,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنزِلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">send down</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to us</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَآئِدَةً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a table spread</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّمَآءِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the heaven</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَكُونُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to be</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَنَا</span>