<p class="ayah 5-115" id="115" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالَ ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنِّى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Indeed I</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُنَزِّلُهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(will) send it down</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْكُمْ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to you,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَمَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then whoever</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَكْفُرْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">disbelieves</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَعْدُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">after (that)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">among you,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَإِنِّىٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then indeed I</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُعَذِّبُهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[I] will punish him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَذَابًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(with) a punishment</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَّآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">not</span></span><span class="word staticW