">إِنَّكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed, You,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنتَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">You</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَّـٰمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are) All-Knower</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْغُيُوبِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the unseen.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>116<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 5-117" id="117" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا قُلْتُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Not I said</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">except</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمَرْتَنِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">You commanded me</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِهِۦٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[with it]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱعْبُدُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`You worship</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبِّى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">my Lord</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَرَبَّكُمْ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and your Lord.`</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَكُنتُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And I was</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْهِمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">over them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَهِيدًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a witness</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّا دُمْتُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">as long as I</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِيهِمْ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(was) among them,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلَمَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَوَفَّيْتَنِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">You raised me</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُنتَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">You were</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنتَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[You]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلرَّقِيبَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Watcher</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْهِمْ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">over them,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَنتَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and You</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are) on</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُلِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">every</span></span><span class="word staticW